{"tid":2111114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"啟德站搵到二戰時期既炸彈","createTime":"2020-07-16T10:25:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T13:14:36.000Z","uid":52013,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a518a9716c56d4e0746a2b23df5d1238c10f0760","tid":2111114,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:25:01.000Z","msg":"From SCMP<br />\n<br />\nMore than 1,200 construction workers have been evacuated from a Hong Kong construction site after an unexploded bomb from the second world war was unearthed on Thursday. <br />\n<br />\nServices at Kai Tak MTR station were also suspended at about 5pm, after the device was discovered at the site for a pedestrian tunnel on Concorde Road, near Muk Yuen Street.<br />\n<br />\nWorkers called police at about 2.40pm after spotting the bomb, which is reportedly about one metre long."},{"pid":"ddb204efbc36415919335a34c7eeaa955b81f5cb","tid":2111114,"uid":271835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:30:02.000Z","msg":"咁個站炸咗未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3d690722f4dda870417488368d41b8a81fd838","tid":2111114,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddb204efbc36415919335a34c7eeaa955b81f5cb","tid":2111114,"uid":271835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:30:02.000Z","msg":"咁個站炸咗未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:57:19.000Z","msg":"就咁睇unexploded bomb就應該未炸開個站既 可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98261c48eea91bfd7a40c8ab0e34c59f5425d6ac","tid":2111114,"uid":218604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:59:02.000Z","msg":"香港有四千幾個呢啲炸彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dce301db1f978b8b237967afb5f60d7c979fe69","tid":2111114,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16